### Login
POST {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuario": "admin",
    "senha": "123456"
}

###
### CLIENTES
###

### Listar todos os clientes
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/clientes
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Buscar cliente por ID
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/clientes/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Criar cliente
POST {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/clientes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "nome": "João Silva",
    "telefone": "(11) 99999-1111",
    "email": "joao@email.com"
}

### Atualizar cliente
PUT {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "id": 1,
    "nome": "João Silva Atualizado",
    "telefone": "(11) 99999-2222",
    "email": "joao.novo@email.com"
}

### Excluir cliente
DELETE {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/clientes/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###
### ANIMAIS
###

### Listar todos os animais
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/animais
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Buscar animal por ID
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/animais/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Criar animal
POST {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/animais
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "nome": "Rex",
    "especie": "Cachorro",
    "raca": "Labrador",
    "idade": 3,
    "clienteId": 1
}

### Atualizar animal
PUT {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/animais/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "id": 1,
    "nome": "Rex Atualizado",
    "especie": "Cachorro",
    "raca": "Golden Retriever",
    "idade": 4,
    "clienteId": 1
}

### Excluir animal
DELETE {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/animais/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###
### SERVICOS
###

### Listar todos os serviços
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/servicos
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Buscar serviço por ID
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/servicos/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Criar serviço
POST {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/servicos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "nome": "Banho e Tosa",
    "descricao": "Banho completo com tosa higiênica",
    "preco": 80.00
}

### Atualizar serviço
PUT {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/servicos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "id": 1,
    "nome": "Banho e Tosa Premium",
    "descricao": "Banho completo com tosa e perfume",
    "preco": 100.00
}

### Excluir serviço
DELETE {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/servicos/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###
### AGENDAMENTOS
###

### Listar todos os agendamentos
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/agendamentos
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Buscar agendamento por ID
GET {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/agendamentos/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### Criar agendamento
POST {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "dataHora": "2026-08-01T10:00:00",
    "observacoes": "Animal com alergia a produtos com corante",
    "animalId": 1,
    "servicoId": 1
}

### Atualizar agendamento
PUT {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/agendamentos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "id": 1,
    "dataHora": "2026-08-02T14:00:00",
    "observacoes": "Reagendado pelo cliente",
    "animalId": 1,
    "servicoId": 1
}

### Excluir agendamento
DELETE {{petshop_HostAddress}}/api/agendamentos/1
Authorization: {{token}}
